@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rgenev(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(0.02))
    v2 = wp.sin(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs((0.69 * wp.cos(tmp + 0.21)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.38)) * v1)
    tmp = (v1 * wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.69)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = wp.abs((v1 / wp.exp(v1 + 0.80)))
    data[tid] = v0
